---
title: Soy & Redcurrant Lamb Stir-Fry with Noodles and Roasted Broccoli
description: We love a good Lamb Stir Fry with Noodles and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/soy-redcurrant-lamb-stir-fry-81dc09a5-a714cd50.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/soy-redcurrant-lamb-stir-fry-5ce5367173c4810017453bba-c1b55446.pdf
author: Mimi Morley
nutrition:
  calories: 376 kcal
